      <audio_text>Like the NG, a PACK light will illuminate for a pack control failure or overheat. In addition, a PACK light will illuminate if a Flow Control Valve fails in the closed position. Both PACK lights will illuminate 45 seconds after the flaps have been retracted following a takeoff if both pack switches are in the OFF position.</audio_text>
